claim.claim-text:
11. A method for delivering voice-based content and text-based content to a Wireless Application Protocol (WAP) device, the method comprising the steps of: 
establishing a WAP-based connection between the WAP device and a WAP Server; 
establishing a telephonic connection between the WAP device and a Voice Portal Node; 
retrieving the voice-based content from the WAP server and delivering the voice-based content to the WAP device over the telephonic connection; and 
delivering the text-based content to the WAP device over the WAP-based connection.
